# Baseline results directory
# This directory stores baseline results for performance comparisons

# Types of baselines:
# - correctness-baseline.json : Known-good test results for regression detection
# - performance-baseline.json : Benchmark timing baselines
# - coverage-baseline.json    : Coverage metrics baseline

# Usage:
# - Baselines are created manually or via CI/CD at release points
# - Used by gap-analyzer.sh and progress-tracker.sh for comparison
# - Should be updated when new features are added or thresholds change
